import React from "react"
import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"

const Devui = () => {

    return (
        <>
            <Row className="mt-4">
                <Col>
                    First line
                </Col>
            </Row>
            <Row className="mt-5">
                <Col sm={8}>
                    Second
                </Col>
                <Col sm>
                    line
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </>
    )
}

export default Devui
